data.description: This stunning 3-bedroom 2-bathroom pool home is nestled on a spacious lot, surrounded by lush tropical landscaping that offers a private oasis feel.  The interior boasts ample natural light, modern amenities and a seamless flow that caters to both comfort and style.  Outside, the sparkling pool is the centerpiece of the backyard, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests.  This home combines the luxury of a generous amount of indoor space with the beauty of outdoor living, making it a true paradise.
